{"tid":1955242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呢埸歐聯搞死西班牙同意大利人","createTime":"2020-04-02T10:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T14:11:24.000Z","uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd40cc08d227eb5e94812253a63964cb3ce14a7","tid":1955242,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"仲要轉去米蘭打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-soccer-match-that-kicked-off-italys-coronavirus-disaster-11585752012?emailToken=4adeccb887730a865ce250b900038f3fpmYwGn/T6sQ9PB66YgXX5/NE4Gv8e3HNYgLkrqsCWwiKLFl6t6bBrc78S6Sb9T4bNfF5iwOKhobvgkcSKQ8sOiq7JKWRN07gXnwbkHF47HOfbN0uRs6lhcVW1epPmhRU&amp;reflink=article_copyURL_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-soccer-match-that-kicked-off-italys-coronavirus-disaster-11585752012%3FemailToken%3D4adeccb887730a865ce250b900038f3fpmYwGn%2FT6sQ9PB66YgXX5%2FNE4Gv8e3HNYgLkrqsCWwiKLFl6t6bBrc78S6Sb9T4bNfF5iwOKhobvgkcSKQ8sOiq7JKWRN07gXnwbkHF47HOfbN0uRs6lhcVW1epPmhRU%26reflink%3Darticle_copyURL_share&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=d59036b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-soccer-match-that-kicked-off-italys-coronavirus-disaster-11585752012?emailToken=4adeccb887730a865ce250b900038f3fpmYwGn/T6sQ9PB66YgXX5/NE4Gv8e3HNYgLkrqsCWwiKLFl6t6bBrc78S6Sb9T4bNfF5iwOKhobvgkcSKQ8sOiq7JKWRN07gXnwbkHF47HOfbN0uRs6lhcVW1epPmhRU&amp;reflink=article_copyURL_share</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Soccer Match that Kicked Off Italy&rsquo;s Coronavirus Disaster<br />\n<br />\nDecision to hold Atalanta-Valencia Champions League match in February accelerated spread of pandemic<br />\n<br />\nOn the af&shy;ter&shy;noon of Feb. 19, An&shy;drea Pon&shy;tig&shy;gia was head&shy;ing from Berg&shy;amo, Italy, to the big&shy;gest soc&shy;cer match of his life&mdash;along with 40,000 of his clos&shy;est friends.<br />\n<br />\nThe novel coro&shy;n&shy;avirus, which had barely reg&shy;is&shy;tered in Italy by that point, was the fur&shy;thest thing from their minds.<br />\n<br />\nThe whole city seemed to be on the road. In 48 years of root&shy;ing for Berg&shy;amo&rsquo;s lo&shy;cal pro&shy;fes&shy;sional soc&shy;cer team, a mod&shy;est out&shy;fit called Ata&shy;lanta, nei&shy;ther Mr. Pon&shy;tig&shy;gia nor his home&shy;town had ever seen any&shy;thing like it. Ata&shy;lanta was some&shy;how the Cin&shy;derella of Eu&shy;ropean soc&shy;cer, and now it had a date in the sport&rsquo;s most pres&shy;ti&shy;gious tour&shy;na&shy;ment, the Cham&shy;pi&shy;ons League. The match had even been moved to Mi&shy;lan for the oc&shy;ca&shy;sion."},{"pid":"b83d2069cc3d9f71e76a33b1c02a548060c31740","tid":1955242,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2YDMnB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2YDMnB.png&h=efdbc1ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e6d2141bf071292b8fd7f48833ce07ef1059043","tid":1955242,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2bJXux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2bJXux.png&h=26891af7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8477074dca61d309c8ddd3711401a426b30190bd","tid":1955242,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04f2ef8fe0ed852e9966107b6fd4c0194ceb1fde","tid":1955242,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"兩邊球迷係米蘭帶病毒返自己城市。 意大利北部同華倫西亞"},{"pid":"793659e4f85e81cdf76636fe97a570798363dddd","tid":1955242,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"百份報又可以追住黎咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3c79ea180b8d54a7d848bfbdfd4702e926f6ef","tid":1955242,"uid":16465,"like":